'''Japor ivory wood''' was a type of [[Wood/Legends|wood]] found on the [[Desert/Legends|desert]] [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]].

[[Padmé Amidala/Legends|Padmé Amidala's]] [[Japor snippet/Legends|japor snippet]], made by [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Anakin Skywalker]], was constructed of japor ivory wood. The [[Droid/Legends|droid]] [[Information broker/Legends|information broker]] [[Switch]] had a desk made of japor in his office on [[Sel Zonn Station]].

